Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.48,Main Title 1,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Second Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.48,Main Title 2,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 9
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:03.44,Black Signs,Sign 0003,0000,0000,0000,,43rd Autumn Elections
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:10.03,Black Signs,Sign 0009,0000,0000,0000,,Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:13.78,Main Dialogue,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:15.05,Main Dialogue,Aoki,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:16.24,Main Dialogue,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,A dull blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:18.92,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,The transfer student guy's \Ndone something weird again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:20.62,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Did he give up on the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:22.60,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:26.01,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you didn't come \Nto the fish market this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:26.46,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:30.67,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You chose aging as a way to compensate \Nfor the difference in ingredient quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:35.26,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell what you used \Nto age the fish just by looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:39.82,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not enough to reach \Nthe best of what the season has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:42.52,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You won't know that for sure \Nuntil you eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:45.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cook enough for you guys to try, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:46.62,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.16,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,The outcome's already clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:50.36,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations for finishing third.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:52.82,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough to be rightfully proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:59.62,Main Dialogue,Isshiki,0000,0000,0000,,Honored guests, the time for the \NAutumn Elections Finals to begin is almost here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:02.08,Main Dialogue,Isshiki,0000,0000,0000,,Please look up at the ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:08.25,Main Dialogue,Men,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:10.46,Main Dialogue,Men,0000,0000,0000,,The ceiling's splitting open!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.41,0:01:12.21,Main Dialogue,Isshiki,0000,0000,0000,,Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:15.84,Main Dialogue,Isshiki,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gatten Hall as it truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:20.26,Main Dialogue,Isshiki,0000,0000,0000,,The cooking time in the finals \Nwill span approximately two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:23.15,Main Dialogue,Isshiki,0000,0000,0000,,This is the time it takes from the moment \Nthe moon appears in full,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:24.52,Main Dialogue,Isshiki,0000,0000,0000,,traverses across the skies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:27.50,Main Dialogue,Isshiki,0000,0000,0000,,and becomes hidden once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:30.06,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's the same every year,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.57,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,it's still quite the spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:35.45,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,I fondly remember those days...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:39.20,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,That night when I fought \Nin the Autumn Election finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:42.26,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,All the chefs who have ever \Nstood on this stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:44.16,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,has seen the same moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:48.33,Flashback Dialogue,SDad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose to anyone else until \Nyou lose to me again next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:52.04,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna gun for the top seat \Namong Totsuki's first-years!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:53.67,Main Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:01:57.24,Main Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let the cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:02:00.55,Main Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.23,Episode Title,Sign 0332,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}A Sword That Signals Autumn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:36.69,Main Dialogue Top,D,0000,0000,0000,,None of the candidates have \Ntouched their Pacific saury.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:40.87,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,They'll start by prepping their other \Ningredients. Typical, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:44.86,Main Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Working the fish more than necessary \Nwill negatively impact its freshness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:48.45,Main Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,They have to maintain the fish's \Nfreshness as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:52.35,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm becoming excited, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:55.94,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Watching young men... \Nthis is sight for sore eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.30,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mother, you're being \Nrather inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:01.16,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,And your vocabulary is skewed, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:01.95,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:03.66,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your seat in the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.55,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Erina, you should come over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.44,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,She can, can't she, Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.81,Main Dialogue,sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:12.55,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,See, Erina?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.74,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,What a fun family, Nakiri-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:16.72,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:19.25,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira seems to be \Nhandling his Pacific saury.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.37,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the aging was a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.91,Main Dialogue,Marui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What kind of dish will he make with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.28,Main Dialogue,Ibu,0000,0000,0000,,Kurokiba Ryo. Hayama Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:32.08,Main Dialogue,Ibu,0000,0000,0000,,Can you win against \Nthose two monsters, Yukihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.53,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:37.17,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,So many different seafood ingredients \Non the young Kurokiba's prep surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.60,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,I also see ripe tomatoes and olive oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.01,Main Dialogue,Saotome,0000,0000,0000,,He probably intends to make acqua pazza.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:48.88,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Acqua pazza—a regional\Ndish from Southern Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:52.49,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,With fish as the main ingredient, many \Nother ingredients are simmered into a stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:54.64,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple yet dynamic dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:59.27,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's traditional to use olive oil, \Ntomatoes, and shellfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:02.11,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's also notable that the dish doesn't \Nuse much in the way of seasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:06.49,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Because of its simplicity, the quality \Nof its ingredients comes to the fore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.07,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great dish to showcase \Nhis ability to judge his ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:13.49,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,But each and every ingredient \Nis strong enough to be the main player.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.62,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't blindly \Nboiling them down together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.70,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,actually eclipse the \NPacific saury's strengths?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:21.63,Main Dialogue,Saotome,0000,0000,0000,,True, and the Pacific saury's \Nin season, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.13,Main Dialogue,Saotome,0000,0000,0000,,In season!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.73,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:27.37,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's in season, \Nthe Pacific saury won't be eclipsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:30.35,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, it has the potential to become \Na solid foundation for the entire dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.84,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,He was able to select that dish \Nprecisely because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.06,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,he has such confidence \Nin his ability to judge ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.56,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Above all, he's very calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:41.64,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't sense any nerves or eagerness \Ntoward the match in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:42.95,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.32,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you wouldn't, Chef Dojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:49.03,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-kun has faced me in cooking battles \Nfor a very long time now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.50,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Very nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:54.29,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,You were both so young. Very cute, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:58.67,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You knew him back when he was still \Nin Scandinavia, Leonora-obasama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.54,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Obaa-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.04,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:05.92,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Showing off your youth! \NSelfish, Erina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.92,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.63,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,"Oba-sama" and "Obaa-sama" \Nare two different words!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.81,Flashback Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the boy, Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.26,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:16.85,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make him my aide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:17.63,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:18.48,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:21.00,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Erina has a secretary now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.44,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I want an aide around my own age, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.57,Flashback Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should ask your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.90,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like I'm not even here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.72,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already the head chef of this restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.79,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna serve you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:34.74,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I told you to call me "miss."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.29,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.87,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's do a cooking battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:38.61,Flashback Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.92,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, become my loyal dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:42.17,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Woof, woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:50.03,Flashback Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That little girl's dish was better...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.72,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Say "woof" for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:58.20,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Battle me one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:13.95,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Two years after our first match,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.74,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,the moment's finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.37,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.83,Flashback Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,His first victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.75,Flashback Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:25.91,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,We'll face off again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:26.96,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Ryo-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.92,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Fine... miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:34.44,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight you any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:41.79,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll be polite to me \Nwhen I win next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:42.69,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.28,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Heat-resistant film?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.66,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What, it's not cling wrap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:58.61,Main Dialogue,Marui,0000,0000,0000,,It's capable of withstanding heat \Nof higher than 200 C, and cold up to -40 C.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:01.91,Main Dialogue,Marui,0000,0000,0000,,Food can be wrapped in it and cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.76,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,He's gained an arsenal of \Nmolecular gastronomy techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:06.63,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,that he absorbed through \Nhis battles with Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.68,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,His cooking now is not
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:13.30,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,something he'd think up just\Nfrom cooking in a port town pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:17.26,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,This is indicative of their whole\Nhistory working hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.10,Italics Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-kun, don't lose, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.76,Italics Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,No need to remind me... miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:29.27,Italics Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,This film is the key to my dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.70,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.95,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:39.08,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,The one who will stand at the\Ntop of these elections... will be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.71,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,The moon's halfway across the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.57,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Less than an hour left now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.54,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.05,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.55,Main Dialogue,Ibu,0000,0000,0000,,So first up is Kurokiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.09,Main Dialogue,Marui,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.80,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... really his dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.60,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,In a rush, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:01.60,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hope you didn't overlook \Nanything in your dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.91,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Run your mouth while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:08.15,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,My dish will crush your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:13.53,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's Kurokiba trying to do \Nwith that flimsy film?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:16.45,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Something you're very familiar with, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.81,Main Dialogue,I,0000,0000,0000,,Candidate Kurokiba will serve first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:25.16,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,The moon serves to illuminate\N the candidate who is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.37,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,advancing toward the judges \Nlike a stage light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:33.09,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though the light is purifying \Nthe chef and his dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:34.79,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.52,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Still simmering inside the pouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.43,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Very piping hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:42.39,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to make the judges open the dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:45.35,Main Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Now, have a taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:56.65,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.61,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Mussels!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:58.28,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Clams!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.74,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,And Pacific saury!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:04.20,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting dragged into a \Ntorrent of different aromas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.21,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good, my face is going slack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:09.92,Main Dialogue,OS,0000,0000,0000,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.48,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,He's usually so stern, yet he's grinning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.12,Main Dialogue,Saotome,0000,0000,0000,,It's The Grin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:17.13,Main Dialogue,Saotome,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew we'd see The Grin here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:21.04,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,The ingredients are about the same \Nas those in an acqua pazza,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:25.22,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,but wrapping them in a heat-resistant \Nfilm changes the dish's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.33,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cartoccio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:31.72,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,My dish is Autumn Pacific Saury Cartoccio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.24,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,He served an umami detonator \Nin the semi-finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:43.20,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,He followed that up with \Nan aroma detonator, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.67,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:47.25,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Taste it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:54.54,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,So fresh! The Pacific saury's fat \Nis meltingly sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:58.43,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,The seafood ingredients \Nare all extraordinarily fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.11,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,There's more than enough umami here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:03.60,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Such power, sealing such dynamic umami \Ninto this dish through sheer force...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.10,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kurokiba Ryo's true worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.93,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,The Pacific saury may be in season,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:12.42,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,but how could he craft such richness in flavor \Nwithout much seasoning to speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:13.82,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.04,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,What is this refreshing aroma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.19,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's not from seafood. It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.07,Main Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's from herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.57,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:23.78,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,I added them to the packet when\NI wrapped the ingredient with the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:26.29,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,I used this herb butter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:29.39,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,After softening butter at room temperature,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.42,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,he kneaded in finely chopped \Nherbs, spices, and garlic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:36.29,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,The herb butter is complete \Nafter resting it overnight in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:40.63,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,It melted gradually from \Nthe heat in the oven,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.95,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,and its richness and flavor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:46.10,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,gradually seeped into the \NPacific saury and other ingredients!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:50.85,Italics Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It gave an incredible boost \Nto the flavors and the fragrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:54.31,Italics Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's a violence of flavor that is absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:58.65,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we'll see my mother's "baring."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.84,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:01.24,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,In somewhere this public?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:01.94,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:03.86,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That'd be really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.44,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.04,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful Pacific saury dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.53,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,First, it had immediate visual impact \Nupon arriving at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.84,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,You have a firm grasp \Nof the modern cooking trend
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.09,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,that acknowledges the importance \Nof a dish's aesthetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:23.44,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Given that the entire audience\N had leaned forward to look at the dish,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:24.70,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,your plan can be said to be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.88,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,Anchovies are often used in acqua pazza,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:29.96,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,When Mother eats something delicious,\Nshe sheds her broken Japanese
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.56,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,but not in this dish,\N since herb butter was used.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.02,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,That was wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.80,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,and "bares" a fluent command of the language.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.02,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,Adding both would have led \Nto a clash of flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:33.02,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:36.58,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,The herb butter plays a critical role \Nin establishing this dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.73,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,"Shedding" broken Japanese? How's that work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:40.33,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,The mellow butter serves to meld \Nthe flavors from each ingredient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:44.59,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,Its herbs impart a flavor that is strong, \Nyet light and not overwhelming...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:49.95,Italics Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Flavors only made possible with \NPacific saury in season, and no other fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.25,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,That further enhances \Nthe Pacific saury's aroma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.13,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,The heat-resistant film \Nand herb butter both serve
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.56,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,to take full advantage of the \NPacific saury's flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:53.50,Italics Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This is a culmination \Nof his culinary techniques!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.96,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,His singular focus in doing so
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.50,Main Dialogue Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,is what made \Nthis dish's flavors possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:57.08,Italics Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Body...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.08,Italics Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,...soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.21,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,...and ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:03.05,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,All as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:06.40,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Kurokiba, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.68,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,The director went bare-chested, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.36,Italics Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:15.61,Italics Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Sear my dish's power \Ninto your eyes, Hayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:19.38,Main Dialogue,I,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Candidate Hayama will serve his dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.57,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,The hell, asshole?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:31.21,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can win against me \Nwith {\i1}that{\i0} kind of dish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.27,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even being serious about this match?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:34.20,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:39.71,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know that aroma can recreate \Neven the philosophy behind a dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.04,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:42.55,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,A carpaccio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.06,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,An antipasto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:44.88,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.32,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,These are the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:48.13,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,How can he win with an antipasto dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:52.85,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,The antipasto is a dish intended to pique \Nthe diners' appetite at the start of a course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:55.60,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It is, by necessity,\N a lighter dish than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.10,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he choose that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.40,Italics Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:01.84,Italics Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Your ability to judge ingredients \Nis equal to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.87,Italics Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you tried to take advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:07.70,Italics Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,of the best Pacific saury's \Nfresh flavor in the raw,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:11.05,Italics Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no way your dish \Ncan contend with my cartoccio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.66,Italics Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Not after it crushed the judges with \Nits heavy umami and aroma impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:14.99,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let us taste—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:16.62,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.33,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,There's one last step.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:22.44,Main Dialogue,Saotome,0000,0000,0000,,He's searing the surface with a torch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:29.05,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,But that'd hardly enough to counter \Nthe Kurokiba boy's aroma detonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.19,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:42.06,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,My dish is Seared Pacific Saury Carpaccio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:45.19,Main Dialogue,Aoki,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:45.92,Main Dialogue,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.44,Main Dialogue,AS,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious without even \Nhaving a single taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.74,Main Dialogue,Marui,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell just how juicy it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.66,Main Dialogue,Ibu,0000,0000,0000,,It goes above and beyond what curing can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.36,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:55.10,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,The dish became completely different \Nafter the fish was seared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:59.12,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sizzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:02.96,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though the dish is seducing \Neveryone who is about to taste it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:03.71,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:06.09,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait... another... second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:14.46,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,The dressing consists of \Nextra virgin olive oil, wine vinegar,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:16.75,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,and Pacific saury innards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:18.69,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,The rich flavor of the innards \Nfloods the tongue,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.64,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,and emphasizes the sweetness \Nof the Pacific saury's fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.10,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drowning in the overflowing \Naromas and flavors!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.07,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,How many spices did you add to this dish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.07,Main Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.03,Main Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He has only used allspice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:32.09,Main Dialogue,Aoki,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:34.17,Main Dialogue,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,He only used one spice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:35.49,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Hayama's special weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:39.37,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,was to weave various spices \Ninto the best aroma possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:40.96,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:45.09,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,His ability to manipulate fragrance \Nis not just additive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:48.98,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,He was able to highlight the seasonal flavor \Nof Pacific saury with vivid clarity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.34,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,by intentionally subtracting \Nspices from the dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:54.22,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, how did he manage \Nsuch richness of fragrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:57.64,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,It's on par with the aromatic force \Nof Ryo-kun's cartoccio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:01.04,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and it's not possible to achieve \Nthrough searing alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:02.92,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,It's the kaeshi sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.86,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I brushed it over the fish, \Nright before serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:07.20,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,The kaeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:08.93,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Tsubame Gaeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.08,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Kojiro Sasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.39,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you know that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.20,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,But that's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:17.49,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Kaeshi is a seasoning made by \Na mixture of soy sauce with mirin, sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.96,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,and other ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:22.78,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You can make soba dipping sauce \Nby diluting kaeshi with stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:26.71,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's considered an all-purpose seasoning \Nfor most Japanese dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.20,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:32.80,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Fish is hard to sear, even \Nwith high heat from the torch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:36.76,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Kaeshi contains sugar, which makes \Nthe fish much easier to sear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:38.72,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,So he prevented the loss of flavor
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.73,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,that would have resulted from \Na more prolonged exposure to heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:46.14,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,The surface fat of the fish \Nand the sugars in the kaeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.37,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,sizzle and bubble from the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:51.51,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I managed to demonstrate \Ntwo theoretically opposing principles—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:55.49,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,the subtraction of aroma and its emphasis— \Nin unison with this single dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:58.07,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Kurokiba Ryo and Hayama Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:01.33,Italics Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,They both evolved because \Nof their previous match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:05.60,Italics Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Kurokiba Ryo wields a massive sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:11.05,Italics Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He further improved the explosive, \Nappetizing power of his dish at the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:14.54,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,In contrast, the duck dish that \NHayama Akira served at the semi-finals
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.68,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,was a brilliant feast of spices.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:20.14,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a finely crafted, ornate sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.13,Italics Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But look at Hayama tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:27.04,Italics Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Refinement through \Ndifferentiation and selection
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:31.02,Italics Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,has produced a blade that is as sharp \Nand fine as a well-honed rapier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:47.25,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,What did you call me before? \NA one-trick pony with spices?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.92,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,This is what it means to have \Nabsolute mastery over aroma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:56.13,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the master of fragrance, \NHayama Akira's, true worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.35,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,This Pacific saury is such a pure force!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:00.05,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,It unleashes its flavor... with no pretense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.10,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,A well-aimed arrow is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:05.85,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:10.27,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,The director's gone bare-chested again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:11.22,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.73,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,The moon's starting to set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:15.15,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Soma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:17.96,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira, you're running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.12,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.13,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.84,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,This is irresistible to anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.64,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,who eats rice on a daily basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.39,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough to make you smile \Npurely from reflex
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.18,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,from the sight of it,\N and the destructive aroma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:45.52,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's Salted Rice Bran Pacific Saury Rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.45,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Salted rice bran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.27,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Pickled with salted rice bran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.73,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,So he didn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:50.69,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,It looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:53.62,Main Dialogue,Aoki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was thinking it would be \Nthe worst case scenario
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:55.37,Main Dialogue,Aoki,0000,0000,0000,,when I saw that dull-looking Pacific saury.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:19:00.17,Main Dialogue,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess it looked dull because \Nit'd been pickled in salted rice bran.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:04.83,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear the piping hot fragrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.64,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll serve you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:09.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait. Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:10.85,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukihira-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:13.13,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,What a tease! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:17.26,Italics Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,The other two were also creative \Nabout heightening our expectations,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.07,Italics Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,but Yukihira Soma is not \Ntaking a back seat to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:23.60,Italics Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,He knows how to make his guests \Neager for his dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:24.82,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.36,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:28.31,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.82,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,The happiness of Pacific saury \Nbrought by autumn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.82,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,is spreading throughout my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.77,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,What gentle flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.53,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,He grilled the fish on a \Nclay cooking stove first—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:48.07,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,He grilled it first, \Nthen cooked it with the rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.91,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Such meticulous prep work allowed \Nthis much of the Pacific saury's aroma
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.43,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,to transfer to the rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:54.13,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,And the Pacific saury itself \Nis marvelous, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:56.14,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,With every bite,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.46,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,the deep umami and fragrant aroma bursts\Nforth from the saltiness into your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:02.54,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,This is on par with the Pacific saury \Nin the other two's dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:05.60,Main Dialogue,L,0000,0000,0000,,Is this deep flavor \Ndue to the salted rice bran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:10.63,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. It's a traditional favorite \Nfrom Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.69,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,The salted rice bran \Ndraws out an ingredient's umami,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.13,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,removes any bad smells, \Nand improves the nutritional value.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:19.12,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Some insist that it is the \Nbest preparation for Pacific saury.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:24.22,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm impressed you managed to \Nimprove the flavor to this degree, Yukihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:26.95,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I took a big risk. \NIt was a race against time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:31.69,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I bought as many high-quality Pacific saury \Nfrom the fish market as I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.41,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and kept testing aging methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:37.63,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I tried and improved other \Naging methods than salted rice bran, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:41.66,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to make something that could \Ncompete with top-quality Pacific saury in season,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:46.00,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but I finally found one that was \Nsatisfactory right before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.93,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That was this fish, \Naged using salted rice bran!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:51.71,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hints from Fumio-san's words, \Nthe salted rice bran pickles at the dorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.35,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,All the tips and tricks about aging \NI learned from my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:57.48,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,All of it contributed to my inspiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:01.09,Main Dialogue,Saotome,0000,0000,0000,,He discovered that aging\Nmethod on his own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.61,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,Though we thought it was a worthless blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:08.12,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,it has shown itself to be a fine sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:11.41,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a swordsmith who \Nforges steel into a fine blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:16.37,Main Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,he has created that sword \Nof autumn on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:55.35,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Soma-kun's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:56.99,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! No complaints here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.99,0:22:58.64,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he'll get high marks for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.64,0:22:59.29,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:01.54,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The director hasn't gone bare-chested!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:02.31,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:02.71,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:03.60,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:07.25,Main Dialogue,Marui,0000,0000,0000,,Chef Dojima and Ms. Leonora have also \Nalready rested their chopsticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:08.07,Main Dialogue,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:09.59,Italics Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:13.83,Italics Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,Did the Yukihira boy spend too much time \Ntrying to close the ingredient quality gap?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:17.12,Italics Dialogue,Oo,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of creativity, his dish \Nis not on par with those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:19.77,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he couldn't hope \Nto compete with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:20.75,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:23.24,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Like I thought, the match will be between...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:24.96,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,...Kurokiba and Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:27.21,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to have seconds, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:29.72,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Does no one want more?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:32.76,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.11,0:23:34.22,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Soma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.69,0:23:42.54,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,With this, we conclude the evaluation—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.54,0:23:44.79,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,If it means you'd have seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:47.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to pour this \Nover the rice and dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:48.70,Main Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.65,0:23:54.28,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,My Pacific saury dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.92,0:23:57.24,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,...is not yet complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:03.21,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you this blade's real edge!
